Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕娜子小姐  收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始住在家裡的魔人的魔君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
